traits.desc:
The Skullsplitter has 6 charges (see description for recharges). It gives to Ugluk the following abilities:
. it casts the fame del divoratore cantrip (30 ft, Con DC +21, 4d8 or 4d10 necrotic and 10ft. pull);
. 1 charge and bonus action: casts false life;
. proficiency in Arcana and Religion checks based on dark arts. 1 charge: advantage on one of these rolls;
. all the effects from the attack paragraph.
As a sentient weapon it has Int 18, Wis 14 and Cha 22. DC 18 against control. Sight and hearing in 120 ft. Empathic communication.

